@node "Requirements" "System Requirements"
@next "Registration"
@prev "Release"


 To run APrep you need to have some hardware and software:


   @{fg highlight}*@{fg text} OS 3.0+ (V39+)

   @{fg highlight}*@{fg text} Ed or another text editor.(Ed as standart)

   @{fg highlight}*@{fg text} Lha packing program.
     (As standart required LhA V1.50 - (c)1991,92 Stefan Boberg.)
@endnode

@node "Introduction" "Introduction"
@next "Distribution"
@prev "Main"

 @{fg highlight}Introduction@{fg text}

  APrep is a program to prepare files or software for downloading
  to Aminet.It automatikly generate readme file and program archive
  using two external program Ed and Lha.
@endnode

@node "Release" "This Release"
@next "Requirements"
@prev "Distribution"

 Attention

  This is first program release to Aminet!
  Some bug can occured in this version,if you find one send
  bugs report to @{"Author" link "Author" 0}
@endnode

@node "Registration" "Registration"
@next "Installation"
@prev "Requirements"

 @{b}Registering APrep@{ub}

  @{i}@{fg highlight}APrep Registered Software License Agreement@{ui}@{fg text}

   APrep is Copyright (c) 1996 by Sergej Kravcehenko.

   APrep program is released as shareware.This means:

   1) If you use this program you should register it.
      (I will send to you personal keyfile.)

   2) With this keyfile available all program functions -
      Prefs program and free of registering request.

   3) Keyfile will work with later Version of program.

  @{i}@{fg highlight}Payment@{ui}@{fg text}

   Registering APrep costs US $10,DM 15.

   You will can receive your keyfile only by e-mail.(I have no time
   for diskettes p&p).

   Please send only @{b}@{u}BANKNOTES CASH@{ub}@{uu} and @{b}@{u}US$ or DM@{ub}@{uu} , not other cash is
    @{b}@{u}SUPPORTED@{ub}@{uu}.

  @{i}@{fg highlight}If you want to register , lets go...@{ui}@{fg text}

   1) Print registration from Install script or by another way and
      fill it.

   2) Please wrap your banknotes in a sheet of paper so they are not
      visible from outsize.Insert filled form and cash to envelope and
      send it to me.

   3) Send e-mail letter to addres @{i}dlife@pub.osf.lt@{ui} with this text:

      I'm send to you US $10 (DM 15) cash for APrep keyfile.

      Date:_________          Your name:________________

   4) Wait for UU-ENCODED keyfile via e-mail.
@endnode

@node "Installation" "Installation"
@next "Menus"
@prev "Registration"

 @{i}@{fg highlight}Installing APrep@{ui}@{fg text}

  An Installer script is included in the archive, which makes
  installation easy.You must have AT Installer program in C:
  drawer for this script.If don't wish to use install script,
  create new directory and copy into it main program, prefs and
  guide.

  For shareware version work you must have Ed and Lha program into C:
  drawer and command Path C: in your startup-sequence.
@endnode

